column2: I'm signing because I KNOW first hand how the manipulation and the gaslighting work. Once you blamed JD for YOUR behavior, it was obvious who the aggressor was. Of all the things I have been thru, I never added to or took away from the facts, including my part. I also know that many DV survivors will get pushed to their limit, cursing, hitting back, etc. and the guilt from allowing ourselves, or the repercussions, are awful but, We will OWN it, you can't even do that! I absolutely DO NOT want you representing me! I could never do what you have done, to ANYBODY, not even my abuser!
